<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>3228</hymn_number>
<author>Nico Battaglia</author>
<title>Run to you</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 You are calling
 You are calling me to You
 And I run, I run to You

[V2]
 I need You
 I can't get enough of You
 I come alive when I'm in Your presence
 O God of my salvation

[V3]
 You adore me
 You are drawing me to You
 And I run Jesus, I run to You

[V4]
 I need You
 I can't get enough of You
 I come alive when I'm in Your presence
 O God of my salvation

[V5]
 Ho bisogno di Te
 Sempre di più io voglio Te
 Mi sento vivo alla Tua presenza
 Sei, Dio, la mia salvezza

[V6]
 I need You
 I can't get enough of You
 I come alive when I'm in Your presence
 O God of my salvation</lyrics>
</song>